slide.paragraphs:
 \[
\mathbb{Q} = \text{Set of rational numbers}
\]
\[
\begin{split}
\mathbb{Q}[x] &= \text{Set of polynomials with rational coefficients}\\
&= \left\{a_0 + a_1 x + \cdots + a_n x^n | n \in \mathbb{Z}_{\geq 0}, a_i \in \mathbb{Q}\right\}
\end{split}
\]

